<function>

access:   public

name: allow

param: string, $class, '*'

param: string, $action, '*'

param: string, $submit, '*'

return: bool

</function>

Tells whether or not to allow access to a class/action/submit combination.

* Parameters:

 * string //$class//: The class name of the control; use '*' for all classes.

 * string //$action//: The action within that class; use '*' for all actions.

 * string //$submit//: The submission value within the action; use '*' for all submissions.

* Returns bool: True if the current handle or role is allowed  access, false if not.